## Summary
This documentation page explains how to create and interpret recommendations in Amplitude Activation for personalization campaigns, including defining target cohorts, selecting outcome events, creating item catalogs, and understanding confidence scores. It also highlights common mistakes to avoid when building recommendations, such as using incorrect cohorts or exposure events.

